Package ServerSide.connectivity

'connectivity' package contains the classes that related to server configuration.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Server.ClientConnectionHandler
    ClientConnectionHandler: Describe handlers of Server clients connection status changes.
    Server.MessagesHandler
    MessagesHandler: Describes handlers of Message messages.
    Server.ServerStatusHandler
    ServerStatusHandler: Describe handlers of Server connection status changes.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Server
    Server: Implementation of AbstractServer that can receive Message type message.
    WaitingMessage
    WaitingMessage: A package internal class, used by Server for contains the received Messages.

Package ServerSide.connectivity Description

'connectivity' package contains the classes that related to server configuration.

'Server' project contains all the functionality of the server side.
